CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1957, pg. A10 reads: "The Squaws' Cabaret Party - The charming young women comprising the Squaws, gave a gala holiday dancing party at the Fort Pitt Hotel where they posed for this picture. Front row, Emily Nickens, Lavera Hord, Stella Hill and Alma Davis.  Standing, Alice Sloan, Marion Williams, Lee Shelton, Ida Mae Mauney, Josephine Babley, president; Ethel Chavis, social chairman; Laura Stewart, Doris Finch and Vonda Burwell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of thirteen Squaw members; first row, left to right: Josephine Babley, Alma Davis, Doris Finch, and Ethel Chavis; second row, Vonda Burwell, Laura Stewart, Alice Sloan, and Marion Williams; third row, Stella Hill, Ida Mae Mauney, and Lavera Hord; fourth row, Emily Nickens and Lee Shelton, posed in front of staircase in Fort Pitt Hotel for holiday party
